## Configuration Files Reference

### Key Configuration Files

```
Project Root
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ .husky/                          # Git hooks
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ pre-commit                  # Lint-staged
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ commit-msg                  # Commitlint
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ pre-push                    # Types + Tests
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ .lintstagedrc.json              # Lint-staged config
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ commitlint.config.js            # Commit message rules
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ eslint.config.js                # ESLint configuration
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ tsconfig.json                   # TypeScript config
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ phpunit.xml                     # PHP testing config
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ vite.config.ts                  # Build configuration
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ composer.json                   # PHP dependencies & scripts
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ package.json                    # JS dependencies & scripts
```

### Modifying Validation Rules

To customize validation:

1. **ESLint rules:** Edit `eslint.config.js`
2. **Prettier rules:** Edit `.prettierrc` (if exists) or add to `package.json`
3. **PHP Pint rules:** Edit `pint.json` (if exists) or use defaults
4. **Commit message rules:** Edit `commitlint.config.js`
5. **Git hooks:** Edit files in `.husky/` directory

